core::ops::RangeInclusive::<Idx>::new.doc:
Creates a new inclusive range. Equivalent to writing `start..=end`.

# Examples

```
use std::ops::RangeInclusive;

assert_eq!(3..=5, RangeInclusive::new(3, 5));
```

